{"id":1177,"date":"2025-04-11T00:01:51","date_gmt":"2025-04-10T17:01:51","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?post_type=product&#038;p=1177"},"modified":"2025-11-25T09:39:31","modified_gmt":"2025-11-25T02:39:31","slug":"peel-hoa-hoc-mun","status":"publish","type":"product","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/peel-hoa-hoc-mun\/","title":{"rendered":"Peel h\u00f3a h\u1ecdc m\u1ee5n s\u1ea7n, m\u1ee5n tr\u1ee9ng c\u00e1"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><em>Li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p d\u00e0nh cho da m\u1ee5n s\u1ea9n m\u1ee7, m\u1ee5n tr\u1ee9ng c\u00e1, m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam trung b\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1eb7ng, da s\u1ea7n s\u00f9i, x\u1ec9n m\u00e0u.<\/em><\/p>\n<h3><em>L\u1ee3i \u00edch ch\u00ednh:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>L\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u, gi\u1ea3m b\u00edt t\u1eafc l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng do s\u1ee3i b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn.<\/li>\n<li>Tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n v\u1edbi c\u01a1 ch\u1ebf gi\u1ea3m d\u00e0y s\u1eebng g\u00e2y b\u00edt t\u1eafc l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng,<br \/>\ngi\u1ea3m ti\u1ebft d\u1ea7u, vi\u00eam \u0111\u1ecf, se c\u1ed3i m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam.<\/li>\n<li>K\u00edch th\u00edch t\u0103ng sinh collagen, c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n m\u1ee5n m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><em>Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Chemical Peel &#8211; S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c acid h\u1eefu c\u01a1 n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 th\u00edch h\u1ee3p (AHA, BHA&#8230;)<br \/>\nth\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y thay m\u1edbi t\u1ebf b\u00e0o.<\/li>\n<li>K\u00edch th\u00edch qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh se c\u1ed3i m\u1ee5n, gi\u1ea3m vi\u00eam, gi\u1ea3m ti\u1ebft d\u1ea7u &amp; t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o da v\u1edbi<br \/>\nli\u1ec7u ph\u00e1p t\u1ebf b\u00e0o g\u1ed1c Sulfur 2.28%, Retinol 0.05%, Bakuchiol 2%.<\/li>\n<li>K\u1ebft h\u1ee3p b\u1ed9 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m chuy\u00ean bi\u1ec7t t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 duy tr\u00ec gi\u1ea3m d\u1ea7u,<br \/>\nth\u00f4ng tho\u00e1ng l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng, ng\u1eeba vi\u00eam, ng\u1eeba m\u1ee5n m\u1edbi.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><em>Th\u1eddi gian li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n kho\u1ea3ng 01 ti\u1ebfng.<\/li>\n<li>M\u1ed9t li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 03 bu\u1ed5i,<br \/>\nkho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i t\u1eeb 21 &#8211; 30 ng\u00e0y.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p><em>Li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p d\u00e0nh cho da m\u1ee5n s\u1ea9n m\u1ee7,<\/em><\/p>\n<p><em>m\u1ee5n tr\u1ee9ng c\u00e1, m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam trung b\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1eb7ng, da s\u1ea7n s\u00f9i, x\u1ec9n m\u00e0u.<\/em><\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":3546,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"product_brand":[],"product_cat":[33],"product_tag":[],"class_list":{"0":"post-1177","1":"product","2":"type-product","3":"status-publish","4":"has-post-thumbnail","6":"product_cat-peel","8":"first","9":"instock","10":"virtual","11":"product-type-simple"},"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product\/1177","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/product"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1177"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3546"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1177"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"product_brand","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product_brand?post=1177"},{"taxonomy":"product_cat","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product_cat?post=1177"},{"taxonomy":"product_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product_tag?post=1177"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\